OL,3,CMan confined girlfriend to bedroom
OL,4,Cwithout food and drink for four days
OL,6,FA man who kept his girlfriend prisoner
OL,7,Fin a bedroom for four days without
OL,8,Ffood or water has been jailed.
OL,10,FJason Power, 31, of 8th Avenue North
OL,11,FHull, refused to allow the woman to
OL,12,Fuse the toilet during the incident,
OL,13,FHull Crown Court heard.
OL,15,FMatthew Bean, prosecuting, said Power
OL,16,Fand the woman were in a relationship
OL,17,Ffrom the beginning of 2022 but he
OL,18,Fquickly became controlling and violent.
OL,20,FHe refused to allow her to see a
OL,21,Fdoctor and isolated her from friends.
