OL,3,CMan confined girlfriend to bedroom
OL,4,Cwithout food and drink for four days
OL,6,FAt the beginning of May this year, he
OL,7,Fconfined the woman to her bedroom for
OL,8,Ffour days.
OL,10,F"He would not allow her to eat or
OL,11,Fdrink anything," Mr Bean said.
OL,13,FIn a later incident when she tried to
OL,14,Fend the relationship, he attacked her,
OL,15,Fpunching her twice and pushing her
OL,16,Fback against a wardrobe.
OL,18,FPower refused to let her have her
OL,19,Fmobile phone and locked the doors to
OL,20,Fthe house.
